            <span class="meta-item"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Updated for 2026</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="intro-box">
            <p><strong>Bitcoin cloud mining allows individuals to earn Bitcoin rewards without owning or managing physical mining hardware.</strong> Instead of operating personal mining equipment, users remotely lease computational power (hashrate) from professional mining facilities. This 2026 guide explains how modern cloud mining works, how investors generate earnings, and the infrastructure that makes passive Bitcoin income accessible to everyone.</p>
        </div>
